    • Method Detail

      • greet

        public String greet​(Map<String,String> params)
             throws TemplateInstantiationException,
                    ParamException
        Produce a greeting string from the stored template and the input parameter hash.
        Parameters:
        params - A Map from variable names to variable values
        Returns:
        The greeting -- a version of the template with variables instantiated and reserved words processed
        Throws:
        TemplateInstantiationException - if the template contains non-variables as keys, has null values
        ParamException - if the input parameter contain variables not in the template, or reserved words
